elggpad-lite v0.5

Requires:
	elgg 1.8
	etherpad lite 1.0

Install:
	Copy the etherpad folder and its contents into elgg's mod directory.
	Enable plugin from admin settings.
	Configure plugin.

Note: 
	All pads are currently public, this will be fixed in a later release. 

